commit_message:
fix fast_cast selection

Previously, this tested for fast_cast with plain types rather than
batches, so fast_cast was never selected.

This was introduced in be17575 "Fixed rebase issues".

Fixes #626

issues.title: fast_cast is not used
issues.body:
Currently, batch_cast always selects the fallback implementation, because `kernel::detail::conversion_type` is called with plain (non-batch types), but expects batch types.

Fixing this improves performance significantly; I'll open a PR soon.
